  "keyFeatures": [
    "Local-first Markdown knowledge base with bidirectional AI sync",
    "Model Context Protocol (MCP) server for Claude and VS Code integration",
    "Semantic search with vector embeddings and full-text search",
    "Knowledge graph navigation with observations and relations",
    "Cloud synchronization with subscription-based features",
    "Multiple database backends (SQLite and PostgreSQL)",
    "Obsidian-compatible markdown format with wiki links",
    "CLI, MCP, and REST API interfaces"
